data.description: This 5 Bed 4 1/2 Bath home features a Chef's Kitchen with white cabinets, center island, tile floor, breakfast area, double ovens and granite counters.  first floor master and 4 additional bedrooms upstairs. The sunroom is a great place to watch all the outdoor activities in your backyard paradise. The outside is an entertainers dream with Inground pool, outdoor kitchen, outdoor fireplace, pool house with bath and bonus space above large garage. This home is a must see!  Ask about the current incentives the seller is offering on all acceptable offers before Dec. 31, 2023!
